Given the following program and the specified function, optimize it out via function inlining.. The program is struct c {
  int d : 18;
};
int i_d;
int main() {
  struct c l;
  l.d = i_d;
  int n = i_d && l.d;
  i_d = l.d | -(l.d && l.d) - n;
}
.                 The target to be optimized is int d : 18; (global variable).
